      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i was looking at some of the patterns on these shirts at the mall today... specifically some of the plaid designs. idk why but they feel kinda weird to look at. like they almost feel like they're meant to keep you in a certain mood or something. do you think certain patterns can actually affect how people act?",
