    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"stay relaxed\" thing is exactly what I mean though. It felt a bit too intentional? Like, if everyone is wearing these specific patterns that make them feel \"grounded\" and \"calm,\" doesn't that just make them easier to manage or control? It's like they're using design to keep people from getting too agitated or questioning things. Do you think big corporations or even governments would use something like that?",
